0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）</a>推出了他设计的一件T恤，以支持试图禁止狩猎奖杯的运动 - 他称之为“完全疯狂”的爱好。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ozzy-osbourne-tour-retirement-black-sabbath-3390656">Ozzy Osbourne：摇滚乐表演者与众不同</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（11月18日）由Ban Trophy Hunting UK出版了一个视频剪辑，显示Osbourne和他的妻子Sharon在他的定制T恤衫中脱颖而出，上面写着“ Ozzy说&#39;没有奖杯狩猎！&#39;”。</p><p> “来吧，你们。我们要做的就是谈论它。”剪辑中充满激情的沙龙说。 “让我们完成！”</p><p>在通过<a href="https://consequence.net/2024/11/ozzy-osbourne-t-shirt-ban-trophy-hunting/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>后果的</em></a>新闻声明中，奥兹称奖杯猎人“完全疯狂”。</p><p> “您必须吠叫才能杀死一只无辜的动物，然后为自己拍照。” T恤的所有收益将用于禁止英国奖杯狩猎。 <a href="https://campaigntobantrophyhuntingstore.com/product/lion-by-ozzy-osbourne-t-shirt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>买。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Ozzy＆Sharon Osbourne：让我们禁止狩猎奖杯！" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZpMsTm37XAU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说：“我们都必须尽力而为。我喜欢设计东西，所以我为竞选活动做了一件T恤，以禁止奖杯狩猎。政府表示，它将禁止打猎奖杯，所以继续！告诉您的国会议员，您现在要禁止它！为圣诞节买一件Ozzy T恤，并帮助拯救动物！”</p><p>沙龙补充说，他们希望“每个人都购买这件T恤并帮助筹集资金与这些可怕的人作战。”</p><p> “我想不出什么比只是为了杀死动物的乐趣，然后将头抬起在您的客厅里。老实说，我以为那些日子已经过去了。让我们使奖杯狩猎灭绝，而不是野生动植物。”她还透露，由Ozzy和Sharon亲自签名的一小部分T恤也将为这一事业拍卖。</p><p>上个月，奥兹（Ozzy）在2006年担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑人安息日</a>成员之后，以纪念他的个人职业而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-ozzy-osbourne-had-to-say-during-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-induction-speech-3804374">入选摇滚名人堂</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3804384" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804384" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804384" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3804384" class="wp-caption-text">奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）入选了摇滚名人堂。学分：摇滚名人堂的凯文·马祖（Kevin Ma